==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Roaster
<hw>Roast"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
roasts meat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A contrivance for roasting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A pig, or other article of food fit for
roasting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Roasting</ent>⟦br⟧
